        "content": "type: search_result\ntitle: \"afarmerforyou – Organic, seasonal, direct from farmers\"\nurl: \"https://afarmerforyou.com/\"\ndescription: \"organic, seasonal & direct from farmers VIEW OUR BOXES · Convenient delivery to your doorstep in Berlin. Between 6:00 PM and 9:30 PM, Mon-Fri.\"\npage_age: \"\"\nprofile_name: afarmerforyou\nmeta_url_favicon: \"https://imgs.search.brave.com/Xlgphd8tgiEi9aKWUCE8m82R6eEdTc3hpGfSwU7sm6Y/rs:fit:32:32:1:0/g:ce/aHR0cDovL2Zhdmlj/b25zLnNlYXJjaC5i/cmF2ZS5jb20vaWNv/bnMvNmRiZTUxMWM0/Y2E3YzZhMTg5NDgy/NmViZGFlYjMyY2Jm/ZDAwMjQzMjljYzcz/ZmU0ZDcwZGFhMTcw/YWM1MzFkNy9hZmFy/bWVyZm9yeW91LmNv/bS8\"\nthumbnail: null\nextra_snippets: \"Eating healthy, organic and local food is possible... and more necessary than ever. With Afarmerforyou, enjoy healthy and tasty fruit and vegetables, produced by farmers in Brandenburg and Spain and delivered straight to your home.|Also, it is really easy to cancel subscription until 3 days before your delivery. To do it you need just click the option “unsubscribe” in your profile. Gone are the days of having to read about where products come from, whether they are natural or local; having to choose between organic, but with plastic, or regional, but not organic.|We distribute organic products in Berlin for everyone: families, single people, and couples, who want to leave the contemporary system of consumption behind.|The delivery time is between 18:00 PM and 21:30 PM. At the moment, you can send us an email explaining that you would like to receive your order at a certain time (if 18:00 PM is too early for you, for example). We will try our best to do this for you (for instance, if you ask whether you can receive your order at 21:40 PM), but it is not always possible for us to deliver at exact times.\"\nhash: 836159b8b93d1351\nembed_ref: afarmerforyou.com-lpT\napp_id: web\nskill_id: search",
